<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Streak Update</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #4361EE;
      --primary-dark: #3A0CA3;
      --accent: #F72585;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --dark: #212529;
      --success: #4CC9F0;
      --gray: #6C757D;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--dark);
      background-color: #f4f5f7;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .logo h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .logo p {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    
    .habit-box {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--dark);
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .message-box {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    }
    
    .message-box h3 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .explainer {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 30px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .explainer p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>18 Day</h1>
      <p>The Habit Launchpad</p>
    </div>
    
    <% if (self) { %>
      <div class="greeting">
        <p>Hi <%= recipientEmail %>,</p>
        <p>We noticed you missed your daily habit yesterday:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="habit-box">
        <%= habitDescription %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="message-box">
        <h3>Your streak of <%= yourStreak %> days has been reset</h3>
        <p>Don't worry! This is completely normal when building new habits. The most important thing is to start again today and get back on track.</p>
        <p>We've notified <%= partnerEmail %> as well. Remember, you're in this together!</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Research shows that consistency is key during these first 18 days. Keep going!</p>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="greeting">
        <p>Hi <%= recipientEmail %>,</p>
        <p><%= partnerEmail %> missed their daily habit yesterday:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="habit-box">
        <%= habitDescription %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="message-box">
        <h3>Their streak of <%= partnerStreak %> days has been reset</h3>
        <p>Consider sending them some encouragement to help them get back on track!</p>
        <p>Remember, the first 18 days are the most critical for building a new habit.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Research shows that after 18 days, your brain will have formed new neural pathways, making the habit almost automatic!</p>
    <% } %>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Based on habit formation research by Phillippa Lally et al., UCL</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>